"'''The Rebel Club'''" was a comic from ''[[Star Wars Tales 19]]'' where the basic plots of [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']] and [[Wikipedia: The Breakfast Club|''The Breakfast Club'']] were integrated.

==Plot summary==
[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] (Bender), [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] (Claire), [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] (Brian), [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] (Allison)<!--Han says, "He doesn't talk, Sir", mirroring a similar line about Allison in the movie-->, and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] serve detention under [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] (Principal Vernon) for participating in the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]]. They eventually escape thanks to the help of [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] (Carl the janitor).

